label: religion
gloss: The kind of religion supported in the place of worship.

label: denomination
gloss: a recognized autonomous branch of the Christian Church.

label: address
gloss: The address of a place or building.

label: id
gloss: OSM (openstreetmap) identifier

label: wikipedia
gloss: Wikipedia link associated with the place or organization.

label: wikidata
gloss: Wikidata link associated with the place or organization.

label: website
gloss: Website associated with the place or organization.

label: internet access
gloss: Internet access available or not, sometime with detailed information.

label: phone number
gloss: phone number associated with the place or organization.

label: cell
gloss: phone number associated with the place or organization.

label: phone
gloss: phone number associated with the place or organization.

label: smoking
gloss: Whether smoking allowed inside, outside or prohibited.

label: wheelchair
gloss: Wheelchair access situation.

label: opening hours
gloss: The hours a place, a business place or shopping mall functioning (open) in a day.

label: email
gloss: email associated with the place or organization.

label: access
gloss: Whether the place is private or public. Access control for the property or place.

label: cuisine
gloss: A cuisine is a style of cooking characterized by distinctive ingredients, techniques and dishes, and usually associated with a specific culture or geographic region. Regional food preparation traditions, customs and ingredients often combine to create dishes unique to a particular region.

label: building material
gloss: The type of material used to construct a building.

label: population
gloss: Number of people living in an area, population of a place.

label: land use
gloss: land use (landuse) type of a place.

label: elevation
gloss: elevation or height of a building or a place.

label: height
gloss: elevation or height of a building or a place.

label: twitter
gloss: Twitter account associated with an organization,

label: food
gloss: The type of food provided in a restaurant.

label: area
gloss: Area of the building or place.

label: fax
gloss: Fax number associated with the place or organization.

label: garden type
gloss: The type of garden.

label: capacity
gloss: Number of people in a stadium or place, or number of car parks.

label: start date
gloss: Year in which the place is constructed or functioned.
